# Build Execution

- Build in dependency order: smoke/test scaffolds, DSL2/configs, templates, launchers/CI/schema, docs/memory-bank.
- Load the relevant domain skill before editing `.nf`, `.config`, templates, or launcher parity files.
- Keep changes focused to the active task and avoid unrelated refactors.
- Preserve existing user changes in the working tree.
- Never leave generated run artifacts as source changes.
